      <title>就业增长放缓，美联储即将降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/fed-rate-cuts-fomc-is-about-to-nod-at-a-move-as-job-growth-moderates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员即将在数月内降低借贷成本，随着危及稳固但温和的就业市场的风险增加，美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔可能在未来一周发出这一信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/fed-rate-cuts-fomc-is-about-to-nod-at-a-move-as-job-growth-moderates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
